  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 20px;white-space: normal;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: top;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;height: auto !important;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4255555555555556\" data-w=\"900\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=28671fe7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTcODKhJo6RrVCln1yCttibCttNNiam2SurfhiaaFYVjbnf9Gv6HJkyqECA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 15px 8px 35px;\">\n   <p style=\"letter-spacing: 0.5px;line-height: normal;font-size: 15px;padding: 0 10px;border-left: 3.5px solid #00b0ec;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编程、推理全面超越GPT-5，但价格不变。</span></strong></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 7.5px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编译 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">王涵</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 10px 8px 35px;white-space: normal;font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.75;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);letter-spacing: 1.5px;text-align: right;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">编辑 | &nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"display: inline-block;width: 49px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">漠影</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">智东西9月30日消息，今天，Claude Sonnet 4.5正式发布，该模型能持续专注处理复杂多步骤任务</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超过30小时，</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">在编程能力、计算机操作能力榜单中占据榜首，在推理、数学、智能体编程等多方面</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超越GPT-5</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.88\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44127e20&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTiamqRicfJ4VI3kdib3LC7ZeYYFxXViaLOOSmLCO0SmiahSGESLNqrWpeNBw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Sonnet 4.5计价标准与Claude Sonnet 4保持一致，即</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">每百万tokens输入3美元</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">（约合人民币21.4元）</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">，输出15美元</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">（约合人民币106.8元）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.505\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d244946c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTk5tc2dQZ674mCge5UQMPHicwcPQAfabJKNK0Y2ygiaMDOHIZcZQVsIJA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，Claude Code新增了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">检查点</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">功能，用户可保存进度并支持即时回滚，Anthropic更新了其终端界面，发布了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">原生VS Code扩展插件</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic还向开发者开放了Claude Code的核心组件——</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">Claude Agent SDK</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，用户能直接运用支撑其产品的底层架构，进行二次开发。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude API也新增了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">情境编辑与记忆工具</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，能够助力智能体持续处理更复杂的任务。在Claude应用中，代码执行与文件生成（电子表格/幻灯片/文档）已无缝融入对话流程。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以上功能今日已在Claude开发者平台、Amazon Bedrock及Google Cloud Vertex AI开放公测。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">01</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">能处理超30小时的任务</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Sonnet 4.5超越GPT-5</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在衡量真实编程能力的SWE-bench Verified评测中，Claude Sonnet 4.5</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">稳居榜首</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。实际测试表明，该模型能持续专注处理复杂多步骤任务</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超过30小时</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78ef85ae&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTO8ibPOGQibMSPmwUnJic4M1oKzjfaxqEZllVlzk78lSHl43cTqrhVjYxQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在测试AI模型真实计算机操作能力的OSWorld基准评估中，Claude Sonnet 4.5以</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">61.4%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的得分率获得</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">第一</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，而四个月前Sonnet 4的得分仅为42.2%。如下方演示所示，Claude可直接在浏览器环境中运行，实现网站导航、表格填写与任务执行的</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">全流程自动化</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" data-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">该模型在包括推理、数学、智能体编程等多项评估中</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">超越GPT-5</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.88\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=44127e20&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTiamqRicfJ4VI3kdib3LC7ZeYYFxXViaLOOSmLCO0SmiahSGESLNqrWpeNBw%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">来自法律、金融、医学及STEM领域的专家证实，相较于旧版模型（包括Opus 4.1），Claude Sonnet 4.5在专业领域知识掌握与推理能力方面取得显著进步。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a0a40c13&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTdOTjaAkGw6sFhQIATHFdZK2HfnT0nFxnEpkd9ZhqU5tU8APqYND90w%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic称Claude Sonnet 4.5不仅是性能最强的模型，更是他们迄今最具</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">价值观对齐性</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的前沿人工智能系统。借助模型能力提升与深入的安全训练，研究团队改善了Claude Sonnet 4.5的行为模式，有效减少了阿谀奉承、欺骗隐瞒、权力追逐及助长妄想思维等不良倾向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8a90a053&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTquqZterQ2eVOR31g8qx1yNQugEae4kzw9qAkpLrYH9RAlCerEWrOLQ%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0 8px 25px;white-space: normal;visibility: visible;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"visibility: visible;letter-spacing: 0.5px;font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><span leaf=\"\">▲自动化行为审计系统中的总体行为失当评分，数值越低越好。失当行为包括但不限于欺骗、谄媚、权力追逐、助长妄想、服从有害系统指令等。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">02</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">推出原生VS Code扩展插件</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code智能体能力升级</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code也推出了多项升级：原生VS Code扩展插件、2.0版本终端界面，以及支持自主运行的检查点功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原生VS Code测试版扩展可以将Claude Code</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">直接嵌入</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">用户的集成开发环境。通过专属侧边栏面板和行内差异对比，用户可以</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">实时</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">查看Claude所作的代码变更。这款扩展为偏好IDE开发的用户提供了比终端更丰富、更可视化的Claude Code体验。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.555\" data-w=\"400\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3aafc2d0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTswXjvZlTiclEDREzicu6jib4OYicJja63DfXlkhgla7hKpX1QlVia9ibR5xg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Code的终端界面也迎来了更新，新版界面提升了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">状态可视化</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">程度，并新增可搜索的指令历史功能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.539\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f21b8a5c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTSMyxSaXjpaK8DlMKr3w77FfXCVN0ibtVACKjMMQ990W24BJdKB9amfg%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">针对需要构建定制化智能体流程的团队，Claude Agent SDK（原Claude Code SDK）开放了驱动Claude Code的</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">核心工具、情境管理系统与权限框架</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。Claude Agent SDK新增加了对子智能体与钩子函数的SDK支持，开发者能更灵活地构建适配特定工作流的智能体。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.56\" data-w=\"800\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4b343f45&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTxZNicgib8qMA1bu13m13xo77qqAsenWYEKHIGl7X2XcXnA0BXFUqQz6g%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着Claude Code承担的任务日趋复杂，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">检查点功能</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">可以让用户在保持控制权的同时，能更安心地将任务委托给Claude Code。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">全新检查点系统会在每次代码变更前</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">自动保存状态</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，用户只需双击Esc键或使用/rewind命令即可瞬间回退至历史版本。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">回退检查点时，用户可选择恢复代码、对话记录或两者同时还原（注：检查点仅记录Claude的编辑操作，不包含用户编辑或bash命令，建议配合版本控制系统共同使用）。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">03</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">性能提升39%，Token节省84%</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude开发者平台情境管理功能升级</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude开发者平台推出两项全新的情境管理功能：</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">情境编辑与记忆工具</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">当生产环境中的智能体处理日益复杂的任务并生成大量工具调用结果时，往往会耗尽有效情境窗口，这迫使开发者面临截断对话记录或牺牲性能的两难抉择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">情境编辑功能可在token容量接近上限时，</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">自动清理</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">情境窗口中的陈旧工具调用及结果。随着智能体持续执行任务并积累工具调用记录，该功能能在保持对话流完整性的同时</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">移除过期内容</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，从而显著延长智能体的</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">自主运行时长</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，该功能还能通过聚焦核心情境有效提升模型实际性能。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.417\" data-w=\"1000\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6366e34d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2Fz7ZD1WagSLhOswBBxyK0SK3yhZBkpAGTJiaL2goFHkNNzLn5Yc3mcPscZrQcPdGjicap32EGlHpMHjfxtMDXP5IA%2F640%3Ffrom%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">记忆工具则让Claude能通过基于文件的系统，在情境窗口之外</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">存储并调用</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">信息。Claude可在用户的基础设施中专设的记忆目录中创建、读取、更新及删除文件，这些文件将在多次对话间持续保存。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">该功能让智能体能够逐步构建知识库、跨会话维持项目状态、参考历史学习成果，而无需将所有内容都塞入情境窗口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">记忆工具完全通过客户端工具调用运行，开发者可以自主管理存储后端，从而全面掌控数据存储位置与持久化方式。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"visibility: visible;box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0 8px;margin-top:-10px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" style=\"border-radius: 5px;vertical-align: middle;display: block;margin: 0 auto;width:100%;\" data-src=\"\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Sonnet 4.5凭借内置的情境感知能力，可以在全程对话中动态追踪可用token数量，通过自动清理情境中的陈旧工具结果，支撑更长时间对话；还可以将关键信息存入记忆库并跨会话传承，持续提升应答精准度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude Sonnet 4.5可以处理完整代码库、分析数百份文档、维护大量工具交互历史。情境管理在此基础上确保智能体既能高效利用扩展容量，又能处理超越固定限制的工作流。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在智能体搜索内部评估中，研究团队还测试了情境管理对复杂多步骤任务的提升效果。结果显示，记忆工具与情境编辑结合使用较基线性能</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">提升39%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，单独使用情境编辑性能可以提升</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">29%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在100轮网络搜索测试中，情境编辑使智能体成功完成了原本会因情境耗尽而失败的任务，同时降低了</span><span><strong><span leaf=\"\">84%</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">的token消耗。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">04</span></em></strong></span><span style=\"max-width: 100%;font-size: 40px;color: #00b0ec;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><em style=\"max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">.</span></em></strong></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语：Anthropic进一步完善</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;white-space: normal;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">智能体开发生态</span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次发布是Anthropic一次从底层模型到工具链的系列升级。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在模型层面，Claude Sonnet 4.5能够持续专注处理超过30小时的复杂任务，这一能力为长周期、多步骤的自动化流程带来了更多可能性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 15px 8px 25px;white-space: normal;line-height: 28px;text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.5px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Anthropic通过Claude Code的升级、Agent SDK的开放，以及情境管理功能的引入，构建了一个智能体开发生态系统，共同解决了智能体开发中的一个痛点：如何在有限的窗口内处理复杂的现实任务。</span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "Anthropic 发布 Claude Sonnet 4.5 模型，其在编程、推理和智能体能力上超越 GPT-5，并推出 VS Code 插件、Agent SDK 等开发者工具。",
